    "description": "Meiho Facility Works Ltd. provides construction management and project management services in Japan. The company provides services for office buildings, government facilities, school buildings, station buildings, factories, research institutes, medical facilities, data centers, etc., as well as work style reform and office relocation projects. It is also involved in providing planning, design management, procurement support, cost verification, construction management, and relocation support; and construction projects for plants and laboratories. In addition, the company offers office fit-out and consolidation; commercial facilities; mechanical, electrical, and plumbing facilities renewal; energy saving; business continuity planning facilities, including location analysis and deliberation on BCP measures for customer facilities services; cost management and cost assessment services; and integrated multi-facility management services. The company was incorporated in 1980 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
